The paper deals with breast density classification using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a problem in computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves training and evaluating a machine learning model, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of large-scale data sets and reader studies suggests that the paper may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
